Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 4.9 25/42] powerpc/security: Fix wrong message when RFI Flush is disable
Date:   Wed, 11 Dec 2019 10:34:53 -0500
Message-Id: <20191211153510.23861-25-sashal@kernel.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.20.1
In-Reply-To: <20191211153510.23861-1-sashal@kernel.org>
